snippet.title: Date Everything – Indie World Showcase 8.27.2024
snippet.description:
Date Everything is coming to Nintendo Switch on October 24th, 2024!

Date Everything is a sandbox dating simulator set in the comfort of your own home, featuring 100 fully voice-acted datable characters! Each dateable object will open up, have their own stories and potentially become your lovers, friends, or enemies. Are you ready to Date Everything?

#DateEverything #IndieWorld #NintendoSwitch

Visit Nintendo.com for more info: https://www.nintendo.com/us/

Subscribe for more Nintendo fun: https://goo.gl/HYYsot
